  "description": "The boundary between memory and perception dissolves. Blend oscillates wildly — high reactivity means every velocity spike throws the system toward full Opsis, then interference drags it back into the grain. Memory decay is short enough that fragments only half-survive. Raise CHARACTER to decide which side of yourself you're losing.",
